fields.About: MyMarket.com.bd is a new online marketplace in Bangladesh; this B2C marketplace has been launched in September, 2020. Throughout the last two years, MyMarket has been observing the Bangladeshi online shoppers & now it has started the online business and becoming popular online marketplace in Bangladesh-both for the buyers & the sellers. We have accommodated more than 150000 products from around 500 different categories on our Site already. Just visit our Site & find all your needs & wants under a single platform. Every day we are adding around 1000 products to our categories. More than 2000 top rated sellers are working with us; all these merchants are trusted names in the online market in Bangladesh. They provide high quality products at a reasonable price to the customers of MyMarket.com. Simultaneously we always check product quality & verify product price in the market before displaying them in front of our customers. The vast range of our products includes automobile accessories, motorcycle, bi-cycle & accessories, apparels, ornaments, watches, cosmetics, perfumes, shoes & sandals, mobile phones, electronics, household appliances, kitchen appliances, gadgets, computer & computer accessories, laptops, foods & beverages, sports items, books & CD, musical instruments, home decoration products & what not!

fields.description: Engine Cleaner, Aerosol Engine Cleaner - An effective tool for quickly and efficiently removing oil and grease from the engine surface. fields.question: What is the return policy?
fields.ans: -	You can return a product within 7 days of purchase and it will only be applicable if you don’t cut or break the product packaging. 	You need to keep the product ID to check whether the product is returnable or not.

fields.question: What is the refund policy?
fields.ans: -	A product can be refunded only if the product is not broken, washed and not used. Obviously, you will need to contact the support team or open a support ticket within the limited time -7 days and fill up some policies like not braking-washed- company info not erased, etc.

fields.question: What are the shipping options?
fields.ans: -	We have Regular (5 to 7 working days, less cost) and Express (Faster, more costly).

fields.question: What types of tax I’ll have to pay?
fields.ans: -	VAT (4%-15% as per product policy) is added in your cost. You may cost extra tax for international delivery.

fields.question: When will I receive my ordered product?
fields.ans: -	Inside the city it will take 5 to 7 working days. If you go for “out of the city” option- it depends on Courier service (We hope it may take not more than 7 to 15 days).

fields.question: International shipping possible?
fields.ans: -	Yes, Possible. We offer international shipping by the help of various international courier service provider (i.e. FedEx, DHL, UPS, etc.).

fields.question: How do I make change(s) I’ve already placed?
fields.ans: -	You’ll need to edit the order before payment. If you want to cancel or edit after payment, you’ll need to open a support ticket or contact the Support Team.

fields.question: What to do if I receive a defective or wrong product?
fields.ans: -	You can return the product/parcel by the delivery person or in other case you need to contact the Support Team within 24 hours.

fields.question: Where are you located?
fields.ans: -	Our head office address: Road No. 03, Block: B, Niketan Housing Project, Gulshan: 01, Dhaka 1212

fields.question: How is the product made and where do the materials come from?
fields.ans: -	It depends on the product and Brands. We try highest make sure about the quality and the best materials.

fields.question: How do I contact your company if my question isn’t answered here?
fields.ans: -	Please Contact to our Support Team or send a mail at support@mymarket.com.bd
